WEBVTT

00:01.485 --> 00:04.801
Madonna Buder, an 86-year-old nun...

00:04.964 --> 00:06.152
Oh. Sorry, sister.

00:07.045 --> 00:11.137
Sister Madonna Buder, 86 years old, goes for a morning run.

00:11.601 --> 00:12.790
Good for you, Sister.

00:14.133 --> 00:17.550
She's still active at her age, that's great.

00:19.111 --> 00:21.228
Whoa, maybe a little too active.

00:21.947 --> 00:23.011
Nap time, sister?

00:23.291 --> 00:24.435
I don't think so.

00:24.783 --> 00:26.941
The sister doesn't think so, okay.

00:27.722 --> 00:29.646
Wait, what? Ironman?

00:29.785 --> 00:32.128
Oh no, no, no, no, no, this is a bad idea, sister.

00:32.252 --> 00:33.398
A real bad idea!

00:33.522 --> 00:34.927
Relax! She's the Iron Nun!

00:35.088 --> 00:36.743
But she won't make it, this is an Ironman!

00:36.889 --> 00:39.225
The first 45 didn't kill me!

00:39.559 --> 00:41.490
You've done 45 of these?

00:41.901 --> 00:44.823
Okay! Do your thing, sister.

00:45.801 --> 00:46.618
Do your thing.

